{"tid":133480,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"腳痕可以搽愛膚堅 手痕點又樣醫","createTime":"2017-02-24T15:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T02:15:06.000Z","uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f3d93361b35bb2c07bd8f5f61499f9eb5b473fa2","tid":133480,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手痕又禁入人地個ig睇"},{"pid":"6467d65aec4438cea84a6b958a125afaf0d02565","tid":133480,"uid":75115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:52:05.000Z","msg":"del apps<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12381bb03fca2226fd10bb7ba52a5f33c8f001af","tid":133480,"uid":59984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"手痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打個飛機先喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733f5704e4d65571dbf348c5d5060a69bb4f44ef","tid":133480,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:36:43.000Z","msg":"用哦羅立英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253bd8237ae47344e3e7b6a59290980f83d3d1d6","tid":133480,"uid":301336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:15:06.000Z","msg":"有人整理左中醫資源的數據庫(<a href=\"http://tcmsearches.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftcmsearches.com&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f6f66b81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tcmsearches.com</a>)，或許可以幫到你。 <br />\n<br />\n到中藥欄目查&ldquo;癬&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n我用過實際有效的方子： <br />\n<br />\n石菖蒲15g 白癬皮15g 苦參15g 蒼耳子15g 荊芥15g 槁本15g 白礬15g ，煮水後兌冷水變溫水泡手也可等藥水涼左再泡，不必煮開。後兩味藥香港藥房未必有，可用可不用。我老婆之前的手甩皮（手癬）就是用這個方子治好，目前一星期未有再發作。"}]}